            <h2 style="font-weight: bold; text-align: left;"><big><big>publications
                  while @ Columbia University (1996-2005) and during my years as
                  a Ph.D student at Lancaster University (1991-1996)</big></big></h2>
            <h2 style="font-weight: bold;">historical note. At Lancaster
              University I focused on high speed computer networks; my focus
              during my years at Columbia was wireless and mobile networks.
              &nbsp;The publications below reflect that interest.</h2>
            <hr style="width: 100%; height: 10px;"><font face="Arial"><font face="Arial">
